Tools: 
- vitest
- nock

* Write behaviour driven tests ie. describe('when ...'), beforeEach( initialize test setting), it('should do xyz')
* always use a real database for testing
* See @test/utils.ts for testing utils
* when asked to fix a test file run tests first using: pnpm test -- <test file path>